>\n<br />\n唯有開新POST <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/688694/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/688694/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"睇得明喎其實"},{"pid":"69f602db2924323190ed9f634402022f0a4dd55d","tid":688113,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c48ca90e3161c30134500f93294a7e212b5f934","tid":688113,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b7936574ccb313d2b0a3ff0c8fe4b16ce07e058","tid":688113,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"因TITLE受到連登仔 強烈反感<br />\n<br />\n唯有開新POST <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/688694/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/688694/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"睇得明喎其實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"咪係囉，我一睇中國地區已經知講緊山陰山陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}